Shadowbox is a media-viewer script for web pages that allows content to be
viewed without navigating away from the original linking page.

Author:      Michael J. I. Jackson <mjijackson@gmail.com>
Copyright:   2007 Michael J. I. Jackson

You can view a demonstration of Shadowbox at http://mjijackson.com/shadowbox

You can download Shadowbox from http://mjijackson.com/shadowbox/download.php

If you find Shadowbox useful, please consider making a donation http://mjijackson.com/shadowbox/#tip

